translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ジャハルッカスを倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスはコールドスリープを開けまくり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance opened multiple cold sleep chambers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王テラを発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Discovered Queen Terra.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 数千年ぶりの女王降臨にホルス達は大喜び
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus and others were overjoyed at the queen's descent for the first time in thousands of years.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テラは人類との共存を希望しその橋渡しをランスに依頼
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Terra wished for coexistence with humanity and entrusted Lance to be the mediator.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ３ヶ月ぶりに巨大戦艦遺跡から出たランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and company emerged from the gigantic battleship ruins after three months.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 法王クルックーと迎えに来ていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pope Krukku had come to welcome them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、人類は滅亡の危機に立たされていると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He said humanity is now facing the threat of extinction.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自由都市のＣＩＴＹにあるランス城に帰還した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Returned to Lance Castle in the free city, CITY.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍に攻められ世界が危機に陥っている状況を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heard about the situation where the world is in crisis due to an invasion by the demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 面倒くさがるランスだがシィルが何とか説得を行う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though Lance found it bothersome, Seere managed to persuade him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍の状況を知り魔人サテラが魔物界に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Learning of the demon army's situation, the demon Satela returned to the demon realm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、夜
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫を抱く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Holding Kaori-hime.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：香姫のエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Erotic scene of Kaori-hime.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に世界各国から首脳陣が集まり会議が行われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Leaders from various countries gathered at Lance Castle for a conference.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: が長年の因縁もあり協力関係は作れず混乱状態
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, due to longstanding grudges, no cooperative relations could be formed, resulting in confusion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスがリーダーになり世界をまとめると宣言
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance declared he would become the leader and unite the world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：荒れる円卓会議"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Turbulent round table conference.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍がランス城の近くに来たとの報告が入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A report came in that the demon army was approaching near Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが直に倒しに行きます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance decided to go directly to defeat them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各国精鋭で美女を一人ずつメンバーに出せとランスが言ったが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance demanded that each country send one beautiful elite member,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 集まったメンバーは姫様達だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The gathered members turned out to be princesses.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜カード：リア、シーラ、マジック＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cards: Ria, Sheila, Magic.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城側の平原
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plains near Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵の説明、魔物はリーダーを倒すと霧散する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Explanation of monster soldiers: when the leader is defeated, the monsters disperse into mist.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙うは魔物将軍だけだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The target is only the monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Choice:

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　せっかくだから正面突破
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Since it's a special occasion, break through the front.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　迂回してボスを倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Go around and defeat the boss.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 正面突破で戦う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fight with a frontal assault.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様の強さを内外に示すのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Show my strength to both friend and foe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここは俺様の庭みたいな場所だからな、地理には詳しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This place is like my backyard; I'm very familiar with the geography.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 森を抜けて敵軍団の後ろ側に出るぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll go through the forest and come out behind the enemy troops.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指揮している魔物隊長や魔物将軍やらは臆病だからいつも後ろの安全な所にいるからな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster captains and generals commanding are cowardly, so they're always in the safe rear positions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこを襲う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll attack there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リアの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ria's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 世界征服してダーリンにプレゼントしたかったのに・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wanted to conquer the world and present it to my darling...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 子供の話、まだ見に来てくれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Talking about the child, still hasn't come to see me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sheila's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラとシィルの奴隷１号２号紹介
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Introduction of slaves No. 1 and 2, Sheila and Seere.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 二人は仲良しになる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The two become close friends.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジックの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Magic's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスとは距離を置く宣言、もう好きでもなんでもないわと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Declared to keep distance from Lance, saying she no longer likes him or anything.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫、エロをした後の会話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kaori-hime, conversation after the erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 立派になった香、妹が兄ばなれしたようで不安なランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The grown-up Kaori; Lance is uneasy as his little sister seems to have distanced herself from her big brother.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 森の中、かなみが偵察で魔物将軍を見つけた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the forest, Kanami found the monster general while scouting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が襲いかかる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘　魔物将軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle: Monster General.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍が倒れると魔物兵は逃げて行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When the monster general is defeated, the monster soldiers flee.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 腹の中からアールコートを保護
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescued Arcoat from inside the belly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そしてエロ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And then an erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜ＣＧ：アールコートのエロ＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Erotic scene of Arcoat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍を撃破して上機嫌なランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance is in a good mood after defeating the monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 参謀本部にアールコートが入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arcoat joins the command headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地の戦況説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Explanation of the battle situation in various regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 十数体の魔人の存在、ボスはケイブリス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are over a dozen demon generals; the boss is Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まずはカラーの森を最初に救う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: First, we will rescue the Color Forest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自由都市、ゼスを通過して
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Passing through the free city, Zes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ジャハルッカスを倒した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Defeated Jaharukkasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスはコールドスリープを開けまくり
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance opened multiple cold sleep chambers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 女王テラを発見した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Discovered Queen Terra.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 数千年ぶりの女王降臨にホルス達は大喜び
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Horus and others were overjoyed at the queen's descent for the first time in thousands of years.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: テラは人類との共存を希望しその橋渡しをランスに依頼
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Terra wished for coexistence with humanity and entrusted Lance to be the mediator.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ３ヶ月ぶりに巨大戦艦遺跡から出たランス達
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and company emerged from the gigantic battleship ruins after three months.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 法王クルックーと迎えに来ていた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Pope Krukku had come to welcome them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 今、人類は滅亡の危機に立たされていると
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: He said humanity is now facing the threat of extinction.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自由都市のＣＩＴＹにあるランス城に帰還した
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Returned to Lance Castle in the free city, CITY.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍に攻められ世界が危機に陥っている状況を聞く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Heard about the situation where the world is in crisis due to an invasion by the demon army.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 面倒くさがるランスだがシィルが何とか説得を行う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Though Lance found it bothersome, Seere managed to persuade him.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍の状況を知り魔人サテラが魔物界に戻る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Learning of the demon army's situation, the demon Satela returned to the demon realm.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城、夜
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle, night.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫を抱く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Holding Kaori-hime.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：香姫のエロ"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Erotic scene of Kaori-hime.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城に世界各国から首脳陣が集まり会議が行われる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Leaders from various countries gathered at Lance Castle for a conference.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: が長年の因縁もあり協力関係は作れず混乱状態
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: However, due to longstanding grudges, no cooperative relations could be formed, resulting in confusion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスがリーダーになり世界をまとめると宣言
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance declared he would become the leader and unite the world.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: "ＣＧ：荒れる円卓会議"
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Turbulent round table conference.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍がランス城の近くに来たとの報告が入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A report came in that the demon army was approaching near Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスが直に倒しに行きます
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance decided to go directly to defeat them.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各国精鋭で美女を一人ずつメンバーに出せとランスが言ったが
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance demanded that each country send one beautiful elite member,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 集まったメンバーは姫様達だった
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The gathered members turned out to be princesses.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜カード：リア、シーラ、マジック＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Cards: Ria, Sheila, Magic.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城側の平原
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The plains near Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物兵の説明、魔物はリーダーを倒すと霧散する
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Explanation of monster soldiers: when the leader is defeated, the monsters disperse into mist.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 狙うは魔物将軍だけだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The target is only the monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞選択
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Choice:

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　せっかくだから正面突破
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Since it's a special occasion, break through the front.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞　迂回してボスを倒す
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: > Go around and defeat the boss.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 正面突破で戦う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Fight with a frontal assault.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 俺様の強さを内外に示すのだ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Show my strength to both friend and foe.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ここは俺様の庭みたいな場所だからな、地理には詳しい
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: This place is like my backyard; I'm very familiar with the geography.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 森を抜けて敵軍団の後ろ側に出るぞ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll go through the forest and come out behind the enemy troops.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 指揮している魔物隊長や魔物将軍やらは臆病だからいつも後ろの安全な所にいるからな
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The monster captains and generals commanding are cowardly, so they're always in the safe rear positions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そこを襲う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: We'll attack there.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: リアの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ria's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 世界征服してダーリンにプレゼントしたかったのに・・
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I wanted to conquer the world and present it to my darling...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 子供の話、まだ見に来てくれない
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Talking about the child, still hasn't come to see me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sheila's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: シーラとシィルの奴隷１号２号紹介
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Introduction of slaves No. 1 and 2, Sheila and Seere.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 二人は仲良しになる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The two become close friends.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: マジックの初期説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Magic's initial explanation.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランスとは距離を置く宣言、もう好きでもなんでもないわと
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Declared to keep distance from Lance, saying she no longer likes him or anything.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 香姫、エロをした後の会話
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Kaori-hime, conversation after the erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 立派になった香、妹が兄ばなれしたようで不安なランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The grown-up Kaori; Lance is uneasy as his little sister seems to have distanced herself from her big brother.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 森の中、かなみが偵察で魔物将軍を見つけた
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: In the forest, Kanami found the monster general while scouting.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス達が襲いかかる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance and the others attack.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＞戦闘　魔物将軍
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Battle: Monster General.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍が倒れると魔物兵は逃げて行く
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: When the monster general is defeated, the monster soldiers flee.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 腹の中からアールコートを保護
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Rescued Arcoat from inside the belly.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そしてエロ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: And then an erotic scene.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ＜ＣＧ：アールコートのエロ＞
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: CG: Erotic scene of Arcoat.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ランス城
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance Castle.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔物将軍を撃破して上機嫌なランス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Lance is in a good mood after defeating the monster general.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 参謀本部にアールコートが入る
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Arcoat joins the command headquarters.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 各地の戦況説明
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Explanation of the battle situation in various regions.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 十数体の魔人の存在、ボスはケイブリス
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: There are over a dozen demon generals; the boss is Cavebris.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: まずはカラーの森を最初に救う
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: First, we will rescue the Color Forest.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 自由都市、ゼスを通過して
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Passing through the free city, Zes.
